mmands; - manual QA checklist; - estimated order; - definition of done.  After all subagent reviews return, consolidate them into a single implementation queue.  The implementation queue must include: - task ID; - workstream; - branch name; - target repo; - allowed files; - forbidden files; - exact implementation goal; - validation commands; - status file path; - dependency on other tasks; - approval needed or not.  Do not edit files. Do not run destructive commands. Do not create commits. End by asking me to approve which workstream to start first.'
